### Character Legend

|Character|Purpose|Example Usage|
|---|---|---|
|`â”Œâ”€â”â””â”€â”˜â”‚`|Primary containers|Main panels, modals|
|`â•”â•â•—â•šâ•â•â•‘`|Emphasized containers|Headers, important sections|
|`â•­â”€â•®â•°â”€â•¯â”‚`|Rounded containers|Cards, soft boundaries|
|`â”¬â”´â”¼â”œâ”¤`|Dividers/Connectors|Grid layouts, separators|
|`â–“â–’â–‘`|Fill patterns|Progress bars, disabled states|
|`â–²â–¼â—„â–º`|Directional indicators|Arrows, sort indicators|
|`â—â—‹â—†â—‡`|Status indicators|Bullets, selection states|

